\cb5 The eruption of Soufri\'e8re Hills Volcano started on 18 July 1995. The early days of the eruption where characterised by relatively small, phreatic eruptions driven by steam fracturing and exploding parts of the volcano. A lot of people got in their cars and tried to leave in a hurry when those early explosions happened.\cb1 \
